24:49.405 --> 24:51.197
Move the car, Nicky, the car!

25:13.921 --> 25:15.805
You got some aspirin?

25:37.369 --> 25:39.829
I'm sorry. It was an emergency.

26:08.067 --> 26:10.944
- You sure this is a good idea?
- Daddy.

26:11.153 --> 26:13.446
Isn't she beautiful?

26:13.656 --> 26:17.033
Yeah, but who's that with her?

26:19.912 --> 26:22.330
What do you see in this guy?

26:22.540 --> 26:25.291
He has everything I ever wanted.

26:25.501 --> 26:27.252
You don't ask for much, do you?

26:28.128 --> 26:30.296
Did your mother tell you
everything you need to know?

26:30.506 --> 26:31.965
She taught me how to fry bananas.

26:32.174 --> 26:33.049
Oh, beautiful!

26:33.259 --> 26:36.386
You'll end up working
in a Spanish restaurant.

26:45.980 --> 26:47.355
You're not pregnant, are you?

26:47.565 --> 26:50.066
Daddy! The way you brought me up?

26:50.276 --> 26:51.859
All right.

27:06.584 --> 27:10.044
Welcome, Allison. Welcome, Julio.

27:17.845 --> 27:21.306
Julio Vidal O'Campo,
will you have Allison

27:22.725 --> 27:26.060
Juliana Capuletti, to be your wife,

27:27.229 --> 27:28.813
to live together in the
covenant of marriage?

27:29.023 --> 27:30.648
Shhh!

27:30.858 --> 27:34.277
Will you love her, comfort her,
honor her and keep her

27:34.486 --> 27:36.779
