What's your problem?

28:15.319 --> 28:17.153
Hey!

28:17.363 --> 28:19.155
Whoo!

28:19.406 --> 28:20.615
Hey!

28:24.328 --> 28:25.662
Whoo!

28:32.252 --> 28:35.213
Why didn't he fix the walk?
It's been this way for months!

29:10.582 --> 29:13.459
Why can't you make everybody happy
and shake hands with this kid?

29:13.669 --> 29:15.461
- Not me.
- Shake hands with him.

29:15.671 --> 29:17.547
Go ahead.

29:20.092 --> 29:21.217
Look at him, look at him.

29:21.427 --> 29:23.553
If I look at him, I won't shake hands!

29:23.846 --> 29:26.013
Look at him. Go ahead.

29:28.350 --> 29:30.727
Now look, Julio.
We're family now, all right?

29:30.936 --> 29:33.730
Just do the right thing.
Make Allison happy.

29:33.939 --> 29:35.690
She's a great girl.

29:35.899 --> 29:39.318
I know, I lived with her for 18 years.

29:39.862 --> 29:42.363
Can I call you dad?

29:44.992 --> 29:48.828
Oh, it's wonderful to
see you two get along.

29:57.087 --> 29:59.213
Good-bye, honey!

