Hey, what are we doin' here,
my glass is empty.

30:12.561 --> 30:14.228
Come on, will ya?

30:33.332 --> 30:34.749
Wow.

30:35.876 --> 30:37.668
This is it.

30:37.878 --> 30:41.005
Yeah, our first motel room.

31:13.330 --> 31:16.690
